 • Driving in dusty conditions

 • Driving short distances in extremely cold weather < 16 km / 10 miles

 • Driving extremely short distances < 8 km / 5 miles

 • Driving in extremely hot conditions > 35 °C / 95 °F

 • Driving in mountainous regions

 • Frequent start/stop driving

 • Prolonged idling

 • Frequent trailer towing

 • Driving in muddy conditions

 • Frequent driving on de-iced roads

