 HaynesPro provides maintenance information which conforms to the OEM data.

 Vehicle distributors may provide region-specific maintenance; this may differ slightly from the OEM data.

 To facilitate fair competition, we provide dealer-specific information when possible.

 The options are given as the OEM Schedule and the Dealer Schedule.

 Operating conditions

 Severe conditions apply when the vehicle is operated under one or more of the following conditions:

 • Driving on rough and/or muddy roads

 • Driving in dusty conditions

 • Driving in wet conditions and/or on salted roads

 • Driving in mountainous regions

 • Carrying heavy loads

 • Driving short distances in extremely cold weather

 • Taxi, police or delivery/commercial services

 • Prolonged idling

 • High-speed driving

