 Select the ''CLASSIC'' menu from the list

 Scroll through the menu until ''Total distance'' appears

 Press and hold button (2) for 5 seconds

 Within 1.5 seconds

 Press and hold the ''OK'' button for at least 3 seconds

 The menu with ''VEHICLE DATA'', ''DYNAMOMETER TEST'' and ''ASSYST PLUS'' appears

 Turn the ignition key to position ''2''

 Scroll through the menu on the display using the navigation touch pad (1)

 Select ''Remote functions''

 Press the ''OK'' button

 ''Restrict remote access to vehicle because of workshop operations?'' is displayed

 Press the ''OK'' button

 ''Remote functions restricted, service required'' is displayed

 Check that the ''Mercedes me'' symbol is not displayed

 ZEnlarge

 The remote services have been disabled

 Press button (2) repeatedly

 Turn the ignition key to position ''0''

 The procedure is complete

