 Condition Based Servicing

 The vehicle is equipped with ''Condition Based Servicing''

 Condition Based Servicing is a system that monitors the wear of certain vehicle components to determine when items are due for inspection/renewal

 Once an item has reached a preset limit, a corresponding icon will be shown on the vehicle''s display

 Note: This information is also stored in the vehicle''s ignition key; however a BMW key reader is required to retrieve this information

 A maintenance service contains the Standard Operations, plus the items indicated on the vehicle''s display

 The oil service intervals are shown by a code or as a time/distance dependent interval

 The oil service intervals can be accessed via the car menu or by using a diagnostic tool

 Note: Factory preset oil service intervals, valid for Europe: (SA8KA, SA8KB)

 Note: Depending on market requirements, the oil change intervals can be recoded

 Oil service and Time interval:

 Diesel engines with standard oil interval:

 • 30,000 km (20,000 miles)/24 months (SA8KA)

 Diesel engines with reduced oil interval:

 • 25,000 km (17,000 miles)/24 months (SA8KB)

 Diesel engines with reduced oil interval (low-grade fuels):

 • 20,000 km (12,000 miles)/18 months (SA8KH)

 • 15,000 km (10,000 miles)/18 months (SA8KK)

 • 15,000 km (10,000 miles)/12 months (SA8KL)

 • 12,000 km (8,000 miles)/12 months (SA8KM)

 • 8,000 km (5,000 miles)/12 months (SA8KP)

 • 15,000 km (10,000 miles)/24 months (SA984)

 Petrol engines with standard oil interval:

 • 30,000 km (20,000 miles)/24 months (SA8KA)

 Petrol engines with reduced oil interval:

 • 24,000 km (16,000 miles)/24 months (SA8KC)

 Petrol engines with reduced oil interval (low-grade fuels):

 • 12,000 km (8,000 miles)/24 months (SA8KE, SA988)

 • 20,000 km (12,000 miles)/18 months (SA8KH)

 • 15,000 km (10,000 miles)/18 months (SA8KK)

 • 15,000 km (10,000 miles)/12 months (SA8KL)

 • 12,000 km (8,000 miles)/12 months (SA8KM)

 • 8,000 km (5,000 miles)/12 months (SA8KP)

 • 24,000 km (16,000 miles)/24 months (SA984)

